e><br />\n好少出名sheshe</blockquote>Batwoman呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個唔講唔得架喎<br />\n放心，實講"},{"pid":"e6d36b649215672df74cb58d6779aa278e92d9d3","tid":539692,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"Joker同batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f2097ff93ba12ea0824aafbadbecde922756b1","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Joker同batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯有人發起make joker gay again簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b120aa98de5647a186a2b2c09d6b61adc979cfea","tid":539692,"uid":104502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41d8b66ccd9be2fb9fc0c370857484ceecc79bdd","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:12:39.000Z","msg":"第2位：Pied Piper(吹笛人)/Hartley Rathaway<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/scale_medium/3/30334/1138843-jla1980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Fscale_medium%2F3%2F30334%2F1138843-jla1980.jpg&h=d77a3227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHartley係啱啱出世個陣係聾既，但好彩佢既家庭好有錢，所以佢父母投放左大量資金去研究點樣醫好Hartley。雖然冇辦法醫好Hartley既聽力，但佢地研發左一件植入式助聽器大大增強Hartley既聽力，甚至令佢既聽力變得比一般人更靈敏。係獲得聽力後，Hartley變得對聲音、音樂沉迷，並著手於研究音波科技。佢發現一種利用聲音催眠他人既方法，並加入左反派組織The Rogue(無賴幫)係Central City展開犯罪生活。雖然The Rogue成員對佢中意男人冇意見，但佢仍然覺得自己格格不入。後來佢放棄左犯罪生活，成為英雄，並同Central City警局既Captain Singh一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢既能力包括聲波攻撃、催眠、超強聽覺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.playbuzz.com/cdn/16608366-d2fd-4ee1-8e43-ce8f75fc5f58/5fdc30c2-a096-4dc4-81d0-46995aaf0dbd_560_420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.playbuzz.com%2Fcdn%2F16608366-d2fd-4ee1-8e43-ce8f75fc5f58%2F5fdc30c2-a096-4dc4-81d0-46995aaf0dbd_560_420.jpg&h=231c39de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\noff topic講下The Rogue，呢個team既成員都係Flash既反派，隊長係Captain Cold，主要係打劫銀行，得閒同Flash打下交。佢地多數人唔係大奸大惡，會係Central City有危難而Flash應付唔到個陣幫手，算係一班盜亦有道既反派，我幾中意佢地(可能之後會介紹呢班人)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPied Piper呢個角色係基於同名德國童話創作出黎，我覺得佢漫畫入面既造型好撚型棍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/11/113509/4357173-2093362409-fla11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F11%2F113509%2F4357173-2093362409-fla11.jpg&h=d3658834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢其實已經係電視劇The Flash入面出過場，但造型同攻撃方法都相當唔同，劇入面同Captain Singh可以話一啲關係都冇，而且都冇交代過佢係咪gay。雖然劇中變返好人，但之後都冇再出過場。<br />\n希望佢可以係未來Flash電影入面出場，有套型啲既suit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"電視版 flash 都有交代過佢係gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2097220de8a9a325a2450aadc4155d6b96dd5ead","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第2位：Pied Piper(吹笛人)/Hartley Rathaway<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/scale_medium/3/30334/1138843-jla1980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Fscale_medium%2F3%2F30334%2F1138843-jla1980.jpg&h=d77a3227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHartley係啱啱出世個陣係聾既，但好彩佢既家庭好有錢，所以佢父母投放左大量資金去研究點樣醫好Hartley。雖然冇辦法醫好Hartley既聽力，但佢地研發左一件植入式助聽器大大增強Hartley既聽力，甚至令佢既聽力變得比一般人更靈敏。係獲得聽力後，Hartley變得對聲音、音樂沉迷，並著手於研究音波科技。佢發現一種利用聲音催眠他人既方法，並加入左反派組織The Rogue(無賴幫)係Central City展開犯罪生活。雖然The Rogue成員對佢中意男人冇意見，但佢仍然覺得自己格格不入。後來佢放棄左犯罪生活，成為英雄，並同Central City警局既Captain Singh一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢既能力包括聲波攻撃、催眠、超強聽覺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.playbuzz.com/cdn/16608366-d2fd-4ee1-8e43-ce8f75fc5f58/5fdc30c2-a096-4dc4-81d0-46995aaf0dbd_560_420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.playbuzz.com%2Fcdn%2F16608366-d2fd-4ee1-8e43-ce8f75fc5f58%2F5fdc30c2-a096-4dc4-81d0-46995aaf0dbd_560_420.jpg&h=231c39de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\noff topic講下The Rogue，呢個team既成員都係Flash既反派，隊長係Captain Cold，主要係打劫銀行，得閒同Flash打下交。佢地多數人唔係大奸大惡，會係Central City有危難而Flash應付唔到個陣幫手，算係一班盜亦有道既反派，我幾中意佢地(可能之後會介紹呢班人)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPied Piper呢個角色係基於同名德國童話創作出黎，我覺得佢漫畫入面既造型好撚型棍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/11/113509/4357173-2093362409-fla11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F11%2F113509%2F4357173-2093362409-fla11.jpg&h=d3658834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢其實已經係電視劇The Flash入面出過場，但造型同攻撃方法都相當唔同，劇入面同Captain Singh可以話一啲關係都冇，而且都冇交代過佢係咪gay。雖然劇中變返好人，但之後都冇再出過場。<br />\n希望佢可以係未來Flash電影入面出場，有套型啲既suit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>電視版 flash 都有交代過佢係gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有講過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae38012d1f7de4ab3d87c20e2abcbc5aea043ab","tid":539692,"uid":81397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c2f2097ff93ba12ea0824aafbadbecde922756b1","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Joker同batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯有人發起make jo