黎，我覺得佢漫畫入面既造型好撚型棍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/11/113509/4357173-2093362409-fla11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F11%2F113509%2F4357173-2093362409-fla11.jpg&h=d3658834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢其實已經係電視劇The Flash入面出過場，但造型同攻撃方法都相當唔同，劇入面同Captain Singh可以話一啲關係都冇，而且都冇交代過佢係咪gay。雖然劇中變返好人，但之後都冇再出過場。<br />\n希望佢可以係未來Flash電影入面出場，有套型啲既suit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>電視版 flash 都有交代過佢係gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有講過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"好似無明講 但背景好似係因為佢gay 所以有講佢同屋企人關係唔好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5zcXCmPmbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR5zcXCmPmbM&d=JUxhlXtb23yvPGjahr8VzNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2b0c6472\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5zcXCmPmbM</a><br />\n同埋依度一開始 講'being scooped up by a guy cotton head-to-toe leather is a long time fantasy of mine'"},{"pid":"b4a3b2ef5246c5fe494d1db559aee3672c3636cc","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"第1位:Batwoman(蝙蝠女俠)/Kate Kane<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sideshowtoy.com/assets/products/500537-batwoman/lg/dc-comics-batwoman-premium-art-print-sideshow-500537-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sideshowtoy.com%2Fassets%2Fproducts%2F500537-batwoman%2Flg%2Fdc-comics-batwoman-premium-art-print-sideshow-500537-02.jpg&h=301fa80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到dc既同性戀角色，一定唔可以唔講Batwoman--Kate Kane。蝙蝠家族既女人，大家可能識Batgirl(黎緊有電影)，但Batwoman就未必個個聽過，但其實呢個角色其實好值得深入了解。<br />\n<br />\nKate既爸爸曾經係美軍軍人，係Kate細個時被一班男人綁架，後來佢爸爸雖然成功救左Kate，但Kate既媽媽同家姐都死左。Kate長大後都入左軍隊服役，但後尾因為被發現同另一個女人拍拖而被解除職務（以前美軍嚴禁同性戀）。佢話比老豆知之後，老豆唔單止冇鬧佢，仲好自豪自己個女咁大膽。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.paperdroids.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/kate-and-maggie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.paperdroids.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2Fkate-and-maggie.jpg&h=bf4d7d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後Kate同前Gotham警官Rene Montoya開始拍拖，但呢段關係並唔長久，因為Kate責備Rene唔肯出櫃（姐係認自己中意女人）。<br />\n有一次Kate遇到危險被Batman救左，Kate比佢啟發左，決定自己做義警。Batman因為說服唔到佢放棄，唯有比套蝙蝠家族既suit佢等佢可以保護自己(呢個位唔肯定有冇記錯)。<br />\n<br />\n因為Kate老豆好有錢而且同軍方有聯繫，所以佢有一個自己既軍火庫，佢用既蝙蝠鏢都係自家製，有一架自己既Bat-mobile。做Batwoman既時候佢會用一頂紅色長假髮同面貝掩飾自己身份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/7/73958/5802878-batwoman-dc-comics-katherine-kane-j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F7%2F73958%2F5802878-batwoman-dc-comics-katherine-kane-j.jpg&h=93b32c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得一提既係Batwoman同蝙蝠家族其他人既關係都唔算好親近，而且佢同Batman雖然都係活躍於Gotham City既英雄，但佢對付既敵人都主要係魔法系敵人，例如Bloody Mary。<br />\n<br />\nBatwoman係我心目中覺得最型既superheroes之一，甚至超越Superman同Batman。呢個角色拎黎拍戲其實最好，一黎佢係女人又係Les，食正女權撚同LGBT群體兩班觀眾，仲未為左睇女而入場既男觀眾同漫畫FANS；二黎又可以為DCEU引入魔法既概念，我真係惗唔通有咩理由唔拍戲。<br />\n不過華納咁ON9，我惗我都係唔好期望咁多。<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思拖左咁耐，呢兩日比較忙而家先有時間打字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講住咁多，下個po再見"},{"pid":"cbcf985ea83a4766d4bb10fd3ddd3c560ee5e2ce","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T19:33:51.000Z","msg":"順便提下其他我識既lgbt既角色:<br />\nJohn Constantine/地獄神探，雙性戀(包括外星人)，黑暗正義聯盟領導人<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/11117/111170007/4288301-constantineart4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F11117%2F111170007%2F4288301-constantineart4.png&h=22ff517d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThunder/雷電/Annisa Pierce，女同性戀，Black Lightning個女，增強力量及身體強度<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/scale_small/0/3347/1784056-thunder_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Fscale_small%2F0%2F3347%2F1784056-thunder_7.jpg&h=62a030f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCatwoman/貓女，雙性戀<br />\n<img src=\"https://orig00.deviantart.net/a310/f/2014/251/5/b/catwoman_sideshow_art_by_artgerm-d5kc647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forig00.deviantart.net%2Fa310%2Ff%2F2014%2F251%2F5%2Fb%2Fcatwoman_sideshow_art_by_artgerm-d5kc647.jpg&h=862099ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPoison Ivy/毒藤女，流動性向，反派，能力控制植物<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/deathbattlefanon/images/e/e0/0cf2ea8816a214427a316e412f9b8064.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20161026001002\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fdeathbattlefanon%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fe0%2F0cf2ea8816a214427a316e412f9b8064.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20161026001002&h=a4364ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEarth-2 Alan Scott/綠燈俠，男同性戀，地球-2綠燈俠<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/marvel_dc/images/4/4c/Earth_2_Vol_1_30_Textless.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20150107211956\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fmarvel_dc%2Fimages%2F4%2F4c%2FEarth_2_Vol_1_30_Textless.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20150107211956&h=8ce2b069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPorcelain/瓷娃/性別未知，性別認同障礙、變裝癖，Secret Six成員，掂到既野會變脆<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/square_medium/11114/111147698/4251901-screen+shot+2014-12-01+at+1.10.34+pm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Fsquare_medium%2F11114%2F111147698%2F4251901-screen%2Bshot%2B2014-12-01%2Bat%2B1.10.34%2Bpm.jpg&h=de0b596b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aaa59d60792711e6c789c430e76d31a804c2ed52","tid":539692,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T19:34:42.000Z",